"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-03-simone-biles-defends-husband-wears-olympic-gold-medal-21355580\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles has hit out at 'f**ing miserable' critics who slammed her husband for wearing one of her Olympic gold medals inParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American superstar has had another incredibly successful games in the gymnastics arena, winning three gold medals to bring her overall tally at theOlympicsto a remarkable seven.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9935921385800058, \"rank\": 0.006406300969011405, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's won the team, all-round and vault events, and could yet win more gold in the beam and floor finals on Monday.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Throughout the games she's been supported in the crowd by her husband Jonathan Owens, himself anNFLstar with theChicagoBears.\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\", \"score\": 0.9999928980971419, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonathan Owens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old was in fact given time off from the Bears' pre-season training camp in order to go to Paris.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999933149866, \"rank\": 6.6850848387190826e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, some on social media took exception to a photo on his Instagram account of the pair with Owens wearing one of Biles' medals.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.83638377423462e-21, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's Simone's gold medal you are holding, not yours my guy,' one comment read, while another said: 'Why he holding it like he won it.'\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has now directly responded to the critics, replying to one on a TikTok comment, saying: 'Crazy thing is, I put my medal on every single one of my family members and took pictures.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0923925844096558e-26, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So do not ever make assumptions.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like you all are so f***ing miserable.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Leave us alone.'\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were of course plenty of fans who defended the couple and lauded Owens' support of his wife.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as fend off internet trolls, Biles alsoreignited her feud with former USA teammate MyKayla Skinnerin Paris.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9945577023739529, \"rank\": 0.005002699598772204, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999933149866, \"rank\": 6.6850848387190826e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce out of Olympics 100m final after injury and late rule change  ArrowMORE:Fans clash at Olympics as man rips Taiwan banner out of woman's hands  ArrowMORE:Imane Khelif says 'I am a woman' after winning Olympic boxing medal  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"dbpedia\": \"h